details.sectionContent: A perfect stage to convert your imagination into reality.
Give your 3-dimentional imagination- the essence of reality.
1. First of all the student will be go through seminar which is about to give them specific ideas about 3d printing, robotic arm, miscellaneous machines, etc.
•  In first round, quiz will be conducted. Quiz will be related to seminar, intellectual questions, knowledge based, etc.

•  Only selected students will be allowed to enter in 2nd round.
In second round, students will be divided in to two groups.
One group will present set of pictures through ppt & second group will ask the question through observation of that picture. We will provide them ppt.
After that, 2nd group will present ppt  & 1st group will ask the question. While this presentation, we will observe all the competitors & selected few of them after 2nd round for the final round.
Final round will be part identification from picture & also define different functions of given machines.
